						<span>时间：2013-03-29 12:57:00</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="atl-content">
					<div class="atl-con-hd clearfix">
						<div class="atl-con-hd-l"></div>
						<div class="atl-con-hd-r"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="atl-con-bd clearfix">
						<div class="bbs-content">
							　　这是哪个当官的为了混文凭写的论文吧。谁看谁就输了
							
						</div>
						<div class="atl-reply">
							
							<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="reportme a-link" replyid="5555987" replytime="2013-03-29 12:57:00" author="秋池夜月" authorId="54571703">举报</a> |
